143
00:14:04.440 --> 00:14:06.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Harika değil mi?

144
00:14:06.680 --> 00:14:08.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çok zeki, değil mi?

145
00:14:09.480 --> 00:14:11.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kesinlikle çok... Hayır.

146
00:14:19.680 --> 00:14:21.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kazandı mı?

147
00:14:21.080 --> 00:14:22.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tamamen haklıydın.

148
00:14:22.480 --> 00:14:24.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Çok zeki!
-Biliyorum!

149
